            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Juris, you opened up a shop too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "The bazaar is the quickest way to get money for the things I hunt."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xda,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "However, my sales aren't looking too well. If you can stop and take a look, I'd be grateful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Your sales aren't going well?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdb,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Seems like I'm not cut out to be a salesman. Customers haven't been stopping to take a look."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdb,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I've tried using a smile to attract them, but for some reason, one child just started crying."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xe0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "If one person stops to take a look like this, others might start gathering around."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "If that's the case, then I'll take a look. Let's see..."
        }
